  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n I was invited to a channel (as admin) while I was offline. I did not receive any notification about this. Later I joined the channel via link and requested to join.\r\n\r\nThe channel admin now cannot se my request, and neither can they add me as an admin again. My app is permanently stuck in \"Request pending...\"\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\n\r\nI cannot join the channel\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\n1. It should have added me to the channel as soon as I came online, even though I was offline when I was originally added.\r\n2. When I tried to join the channel via invite link, I should have been added automatically, without sending a request.\r\n3. The channel admin should still be able to add me or respond to my request.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\n\"Request pending...\"\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1) Open Status\r\n2) \r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: 1.16.0 (20210827115911(\r\n- Operating System: Android\r\n\r\n",
